<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>تسجيل الدخول - برنامج المطحنة</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial; background: #f0f2f5; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    .login-box { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); width: 90%; max-width: 400px; }
    input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin: 10px 0; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 18px; }
    button { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #28a745; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-box">
    <h2>🔐 تسجيل الدخول</h2>
    <p>برنامج محاسبة المطحنة</p>
    <form action="/login" method="POST">
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="أدخل كلمة السر" required autofocus>
      <button type="submit">دخول</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
